DECLARE CURSOR1 CURSOR FOR SELECT DC_POLICY_NUMBER, DC_DEPENDENT_NUM, DC_NAME, DC_SSN, DC_DATE_OF_BIRTH, DC_SEX_CODE, DC_EXCEPTION_FLAG, DC_STUDENT_DATE, DC_STATUS, DC_START_DATE, DC_STOP_DATE, DC_LAST_UPDATED, DC_LAST_UPD_USER FROM DEPENDENT_CHILD .
SELECT CTY_COUNTY_NM INTO :CTY-COUNTY-NM:WS-CNTY-NM-INDC FROM COUNTY_ZIP A, COUNTY B WHERE CTZ_ZIP_CD = :WS-ZIP AND A.CTY_COUNTY_SEQ = B.CTY_COUNTY_SEQ WITH UR
SELECT CTY_COUNTY_NM INTO :CTY-COUNTY-NM:WS-CNTY-NM-INDC FROM COUNTY_ZIP A, COUNTY B WHERE CTZ_ZIP_CD = :WS-ZIP AND A.CTY_COUNTY_SEQ = B.CTY_COUNTY_SEQ WITH UR
SELECT RECORD INTO :WS-APPLIC-RECORD FROM NEW_APPLIC WHERE POLICY_NBR = :WS-POL-NUMBER WITH UR
DECLARE CURSOR1 CURSOR FOR SELECT APPLICATION_NUMBER FROM RESPONSE_ACTION WHERE RESP_EXIST_POL_NO = :WS-POLICY-NUMBER AND DESTINATION_CODE = :WS-DESTINATION-CODE ORDER BY RESPONSE_NUMBER WITH UR
UPDATE TBL_PM_CONTINUOUS_CVRG SET CCVG_STATUS_CD = 'C' WHERE CCVG_COMPANY_NO = :WS-COMPANY-NUMBER AND CCVG_NEW_CCV_POLICY_NO = :WS-POLICY-NUMBER AND CCVG_DOB_DT = :WS-DATE-OF-BIRTH
DECLARE CURSOR1 CURSOR FOR SELECT SEVERITY_CD, ERROR_CD, ERROR_MESSAGE_TXT FROM ERROR_MESSAGE WHERE (SEVERITY_CD > :WS-PREV-SEVERITY) AND (ERROR_CD > :WS-PREV-OUT-STATUS) .

DECLARE CURSOR_LOW CURSOR WITH HOLD FOR SELECT SEVERITY_CD , ERROR_CD , ERROR_MESSAGE_TXT FROM ERROR_MESSAGE WHERE (SEVERITY_CD = :WHR-SEVERITY-CD AND ERROR_CD >= :WHR-ERROR-CD) OR SEVERITY_CD > :WHR-SEVERITY-CD ORDER BY SEVERITY_CD, ERROR_CD FOR FETCH ONLY .

DECLARE NEWPLAN_CURS CURSOR FOR SELECT NEW_PLAN_CODE ,FILL2 ,NEW_ISSUE_STATE ,NEW_EXPIRE_DATE ,NEW_MODE_RULE FROM NEW_PLAN_DATA WHERE POLICY_NUMBER = :WS-POLICY-NUMBER ORDER BY OCCURRENCE_NUMBER .
DECLARE UNITS_CURS CURSOR FOR SELECT NEW_UNITS ,OLD_UNITS FROM UNITS WHERE POLICY_NUMBER = :WS-POLICY-NUMBER ORDER BY OCCURRENCE_NUMBER .
DECLARE AGENTD_CURS CURSOR FOR SELECT AGENT_NUMBER ,AGENT_LEVEL ,SIT_CODE FROM CONV_AGENT_DATA WHERE POLICY_NUMBER = :WS-POLICY-NUMBER ORDER BY OCCURRENCE_NUMBER .

DECLARE ADDPLAN_CURS CURSOR FOR SELECT OLD_PCIPATING_FLAG ,NEW_PCIPATING_FLAG ,OLD_IF_INDICATOR ,NEW_IF_INDICATOR FROM ADDITNAL_PLAN_DATA WHERE POLICY_NUMBER = :WS-POLICY-NUMBER ORDER BY OCCURRENCE_NUMBER .
DECLARE NONSRV_CURS CURSOR FOR SELECT NON_SRVIVOR_POLICY FROM NON_SRVIVOR_POLICY WHERE POLICY_NUMBER = :WS-POLICY-NUMBER ORDER BY OCCURRENCE_NUMBER .
DECLARE VIEW1 CURSOR FOR SELECT DISTINCT(DESK_CODE) FROM CONV_PENDING_FILE WHERE STATUS_CODE = '95' OR (STATUS_CODE = '00' AND APPROVAL_DESK_CD > ' ') ORDER BY DESK_CODE .

DECLARE VIEW2 CURSOR FOR SELECT STATUS_CODE, POLICY_NUMBER, REFUND_AMOUNT, ORIGINAL_ENTRY_DT, ENTRY_DATE, APPROVAL_DESK_CD, CLERK_ID, STATUS_SEVERITY_CD FROM CONV_PENDING_FILE WHERE DESK_CODE = :WS-DESK-CODE AND((STATUS_CODE = '00' AND APPROVAL_DESK_CD > ' ') OR (STATUS_CODE = '95')) ORDER BY STATUS_CODE, POLICY_NUMBER .

DECLARE VIEW3 CURSOR FOR SELECT DISTINCT(DESK_CODE) FROM CONV_PENDING_FILE WHERE (STATUS_CODE = '95' AND DESK_CODE < :WS-DESK-CODE) OR (STATUS_CODE = '00' AND APPROVAL_DESK_CD > ' ' AND DESK_CODE < :WS-DESK-CODE) ORDER BY DESK_CODE .

DECLARE VIEW4 CURSOR FOR SELECT DISTINCT(DESK_CODE) FROM CONV_PENDING_FILE WHERE (STATUS_CODE = '95' AND DESK_CODE > :WS-DESK-CODE) OR (STATUS_CODE = '00' AND APPROVAL_DESK_CD > ' ' AND DESK_CODE > :WS-DESK-CODE) ORDER BY DESK_CODE .

DECLARE VIEW5 CURSOR FOR SELECT STATUS_CODE, POLICY_NUMBER, REFUND_AMOUNT, ORIGINAL_ENTRY_DT, ENTRY_DATE, APPROVAL_DESK_CD, CLERK_ID, STATUS_SEVERITY_CD FROM CONV_PENDING_FILE WHERE DESK_CODE = :WS-DESK-CODE AND ((STATUS_CODE = '00' AND APPROVAL_DESK_CD > ' ') OR (STATUS_CODE = '95')) AND POLICY_NUMBER > :WS-POLICY-NUMBER ORDER BY STATUS_CODE, POLICY_NUMBER .

DECLARE VIEW6 CURSOR FOR SELECT STATUS_CODE, POLICY_NUMBER, REFUND_AMOUNT, ORIGINAL_ENTRY_DT, ENTRY_DATE, APPROVAL_DESK_CD, CLERK_ID, STATUS_SEVERITY_CD FROM CONV_PENDING_FILE WHERE DESK_CODE = :WS-DESK-CODE AND ((STATUS_CODE = '00' AND APPROVAL_DESK_CD > ' ') OR (STATUS_CODE = '95')) AND POLICY_NUMBER < :WS-POLICY-NUMBER ORDER BY STATUS_CODE, POLICY_NUMBER .
DECLARE VIEW9 CURSOR FOR SELECT DISTINCT(EMPLOYEE_NUMBER) EMPLOYEE_NUMBER FROM PHS_DESK_CODES WHERE VALID_DESK_NUMBER = :WS-DESK-CD ORDER BY EMPLOYEE_NUMBER .

SELECT CLERK_NAME, EMPLOYEE_NUMBER, EMPLOYEE_LEVEL_CD INTO :PHS-DESK-CODES-DCL.CLERK-NAME, :PHS-DESK-CODES-DCL.EMPLOYEE-NUMBER, :PHS-DESK-CODES-DCL.EMPLOYEE-LEVEL-CD FROM PHS_DESK_CODES WHERE VALID_DESK_NUMBER = :WS-DESK-CODE

DELETE FROM CONV_PENDING_FILE WHERE DESK_CODE = :WS-DESK-CODE
UPDATE CONV_PENDING_FILE SET STATUS_CODE = '00' , APPROVAL_DESK_CD = :WS-APPROVAL-DESK-CODE WHERE POLICY_NUMBER = :WS-POLICY-NUMBER2
UPDATE CONV_PENDING_FILE SET STATUS_CODE = :WS-STATUS-CODE , STATUS_SEVERITY_CD = :WS-SEVERITY-CODE , APPROVAL_DESK_CD = :WS-APPROVAL-CD WHERE POLICY_NUMBER = :WS-POLICY-NUMBER

DECLARE CURSOR11 CURSOR FOR SELECT CC_PLAN_CODE, CC_PLAN_START_DATE, CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE, CC_STATE_OF_ISSUE, CC_LOB, CC_PLAN_UNITS FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE ORDER BY CC_PLAN_START_DATE WITH UR

DECLARE CURSOR14 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_CLAIM_NUMBER, CM_SHEET_NUMBER, CM_DATE_CLAIM_PAID, CM_TRANS_CODE, CM_BDOS, CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME, CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE, CM_CLAIMANT_SEX, CM_DIAGNOSIS_CODE FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CM_RELATIONSHIP = :WM-SEARCH-RELATIONSHIP AND CM_BDOS >= :WM-POLYR-START-DATE AND CM_BDOS < :WM-POLYR-END-DATE ORDER BY CM_DATE_CLAIM_PAID

DECLARE CURSOR15 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_DATE_RECEIVED, CM_DATE_PROCESSED, CM_DATE_PENDED, CM_PENDING_FLAG1, CM_PENDING_FLAG2, CM_PENDING_FLAG3, CM_PENDING_FLAG4, CM_EMAIL_ADDR_TXT, CM_WEB_SUBMISSION_DT, CM_EXCP_ADDR_IND, CM_ISF_CLAIM_CD, CM_ISF_REPEND_IND, CM_HANDICAP_IND, CM_PROOF_LOSS_DT, CM_DOC_ORIGIN_DSC, CM_ISF_CLAIMTYPE_ID, CM_SUBM_AGENT_NO, CM_AGENT_REC_DT, CM_AFLAC_REC_DT, CM_AGENT_COVSHT_IND FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS = 'L1'
DECLARE CURSOR16 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_WITTS_ID, CM_SUBM_AGENT_NO FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WM-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS = 'L1'

DECLARE COVCELL CURSOR FOR SELECT CC_POLICY_NUMBER, CC_PLAN_CODE, CC_PHASE_CODE, CC_PLAN_START_DATE, CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE, CC_LOB, CC_COVG_POL_TYPE FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PHASE_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PHASE AND ((CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE >= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE) OR (CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01')) WITH UR
SELECT CC_CURRENT_DATE, CC_RECEIVED_DATE INTO :WH-CURRENT-DATE, :WH-RECEIVED-DATE FROM CLAIMS_CONTROL WHERE CC_CONTROL_KEY = :WM-CONTROL-KEY WITH UR
SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WM-CLAIM-NUMBER

SELECT ST_TABLE_ALIAS1, ST_TABLE_ALIAS2 INTO :WM-SPECIAL-NAME, :WM-SPECIAL-IND FROM SECURITY_TABLE WHERE ST_SYSTEM_NAME = :WM-SYSTEM-NAME5 AND ST_TABLE_NAME = :WM-TABLE-NAME5 AND ST_TABLE_VALUE = :WM-TABLE-VALUE5 WITH UR

SELECT ST_TABLE_ALIAS2, ST_TABLE_ALIAS4 INTO :WH-TABLE-ALIAS2, :WH-TABLE-ALIAS4 FROM SECURITY_TABLE WHERE ST_SYSTEM_NAME = :WM-SYSTEM-NAME AND ST_TABLE_NAME = :WM-TABLE-NAME AND ST_TABLE_VALUE = :WM-TABLE-VALUE WITH UR
SELECT MAX(CM_SHEET_NUMBER) INTO :CM-SHEET-NUMBER FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER

SELECT CM_PROOF_LOSS_DT, CM_WEB_SUBMISSION_DT, CM_ISF_CLAIM_CD, CM_DOC_ORIGIN_DSC, CM_DATE_PROCESSED, CM_SUBM_AGENT_NO, CM_AGENT_REC_DT, CM_AFLAC_REC_DT, CM_AGENT_COVSHT_IND INTO :WM-HOLD-PROOF-LOSS-DT, :WM-HOLD-WEB-SUBMISSION-DT, :WM-HOLD-ISF-CLAIM-CD, :WS-HOLD-DOC-ORIGIN-DSC, :WM-HOLD-DATE-PROCESSED, :WM-HOLD-SUBM-AGT-NUM, :WM-HOLD-AGENT-REC-DT, :WM-HOLD-AFLAC-REC-DT, :WM-HOLD-COVSHT-IND FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_SHEET_NUMBER = '0101'
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM SECURITY_TABLE WHERE ST_SYSTEM_NAME = :WM-SYSTEM-NAME AND ST_TABLE_NAME = :WM-TABLE-NAME AND ST_TABLE_VALUE = :WM-TABLE-VALUE WITH UR
SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PLAN AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE = :WM-COVERAGE-START WITH UR
SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PLAN AND CC_COVG_POL_TYPE = :CONT-COVRGTYPE-CD WITH UR

SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PLAN AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE = :WM-PREV-COV-START AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01' WITH UR

UPDATE CLAIMS_COVERAGE SET CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = :WM-CALC-STOP-DATE, CC_DATE_CHANGED = :CC-DATE-CHANGED, CC_LOGON_CHANGED = :CC-LOGON-CHANGED WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PLAN AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE = :WM-PREV-COV-START

SELECT MAX(CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE) INTO :WS-COV-STRT-WK-DATE FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PHASE_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PHASE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE < :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE < :WM-TREATMENT-DATE

SELECT MIN(CC_PLAN_START_DATE) INTO :WS-COV-STOP-WK-DATE FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PHASE_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PHASE AND (CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE > :WM-TREATMENT-DATE OR CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01') AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE > :WM-TREATMENT-DATE

INSERT INTO CLAIMS_COVERAGE (CC_POLICY_NUMBER, CC_PLAN_CODE, CC_PHASE_CODE, CC_PLAN_START_DATE, CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE, CC_STATE_OF_ISSUE, CC_STATE_OF_RES, CC_LOB, CC_PLAN_UNITS, CC_AGENT_NUMBER, CC_DATE_CHANGED, CC_LOGON_CHANGED, CC_COVG_POL_TYPE) VALUES (:CC-POLICY-NUMBER, :CC-PLAN-CODE, :CC-PHASE-CODE, :CC-PLAN-START-DATE, :CC-PLAN-STOP-DATE, :CC-STATE-OF-ISSUE, :CC-STATE-OF-RES, :CC-LOB, :CC-PLAN-UNITS, :CC-AGENT-NUMBER, :CC-DATE-CHANGED, :CC-LOGON-CHANGED, :CC-COVG-POL-TYPE)
SELECT CONT_COVRGTYPE_CD INTO :CONT-COVRGTYPE-CD FROM TBL_PM_CONTRACT WHERE CONT_COMPANY_NO = :WM-SEARCH-COMPANY AND CONT_POLICY_NO = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CONT_STATUS_CD <> '51' WITH UR
SELECT CONT_COVRGTYPE_CD INTO :CONT-COVRGTYPE-CD FROM PCPTDB01.TBL_PM_CONTRACT WHERE CONT_COMPANY_NO = :WM-SEARCH-COMPANY AND CONT_POLICY_NO = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_OCR_XREF WHERE CX_TEMPLATE_ID = :WM-TEMPLATE-ID AND CX_FORMCALL_ID = :WM-FORMCALL WITH UR

SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND ((CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE >= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE) OR (CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01')) WITH UR

SELECT PM_PLAN_CODE, PM_STATE_CODE, PM_AGE_LOW, PM_AGE_HIGH, PM_WAITING_PERIOD, PM_POLICY_FORM, PM_START_DATE, PM_MANUAL_FLAG, PM_DEP_COV, PM_DEPCOV_STU INTO :PM-PLAN-CODE, :PM-STATE-CODE, :PM-AGE-LOW, :PM-AGE-HIGH, :PM-WAITING-PERIOD, :PM-POLICY-FORM, :PM-START-DATE, :PM-MANUAL-FLAG, :PM-DEP-COV, :PM-DEPCOV-STU FROM PLAN_MASTER WHERE PM_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND PM_STATE_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND PM_START_DATE = (SELECT MAX(PM_START_DATE) FROM PLAN_MASTER WHERE PM_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND PM_STATE_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND PM_START_DATE <= :WM-SEARCH-DATE) FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY WITH UR
SELECT ST_TABLE_ALIAS7 INTO :WH-TABLE-ALIAS7 FROM SECURITY_TABLE WHERE ST_SYSTEM_NAME = 'CLAIMS' AND ST_TABLE_NAME = 'STATE-CODES' AND ST_TABLE_VALUE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE WITH UR

SELECT WB_START_DT, WB_DIAGNOSIS_CODE, WB_TEST_CODE, WB_PAYMENT_NOTE, WB_PLAN_CODE, WB_BENEFIT_AMOUNT, WB_BENEFIT_DATE, WB_BENEFIT_CODE, WB_PER_UNIT_IND, WB_CAL_POL_YR_IND, WB_WP_EXCP_IND, WB_2ND_BENEFIT_AMT, WB_ENDORSEMENT_IND INTO :WB-START-DT, :WB-DIAGNOSIS-CODE, :WB-TEST-CODE, :WB-PAYMENT-NOTE, :WB-PLAN-CODE, :WB-BENEFIT-AMOUNT, :WB-BENEFIT-DATE, :WB-BENEFIT-CODE, :WB-PER-UNIT-IND, :WB-CAL-POL-YR-IND, :WB-WP-EXCP-IND, :WB-2ND-BENEFIT-AMT, :WB-ENDORSEMENT-IND FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_POLICY_FORM_TXT = :WM-SEARCH-FORM AND WB_TEST_CODE = :WM-HOLD-TEST-CODE AND WB_START_DT = (SELECT MAX(WB_START_DT) FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_POLICY_FORM_TXT = :WM-SEARCH-FORM AND WB_TEST_CODE = :WM-HOLD-TEST-CODE AND WB_START_DT <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE) WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE = 'MMG' WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE <> 'MMG' WITH UR
SELECT WM70_POLICY_NO INTO :WM-POLICY-OVR70 FROM TBL_PM_WLMRT_OVR70 WHERE WM70_POLICY_NO = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE = 'PAP' WITH UR
SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS ^= 'L1'
DELETE FROM CLAIMS_WELL_PROC WHERE CLAIM_NBR = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER
DELETE FROM CLAIMS_DETAIL WHERE CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WM-CLAIM-SHEETN
DELETE FROM CHECK_HISTORY WHERE CH_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-CHECK
DELETE FROM CLAIMS_LIABILITY WHERE CW_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER
DELETE FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER

SELECT ST_TABLE_ALIAS1 INTO :WS-TBL-ALIAS1 FROM SECURITY_TABLE WHERE ST_SYSTEM_NAME = :WS-SYSTEM-NAME9 AND ST_TABLE_NAME = :WS-TABLE-NAME9 AND ST_TABLE_VALUE = :WS-TABLE-VALUE9 WITH UR
SELECT ST_TABLE_ALIAS1 INTO :WS-KO-ALIAS1 FROM SECURITY_TABLE WHERE ST_SYSTEM_NAME = :WS-SYSTEM-NAME9 AND ST_TABLE_NAME = :WS-TABLE-NAME9 AND ST_TABLE_VALUE = :WS-TBL-ALIAS1 WITH UR

SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WS-DUPL-COVERAGE-CNT FROM CL_POLICY_COV_EXP WHERE PCE_POLICY_NO = :PCE-POLICY-NO AND PCE_EXCEPTION_CD = 'X' AND (PCE_EXCP_COMM_DSC LIKE '%DUP%' OR PCE_EXCP_COMM_DSC LIKE '%DUP%' OR PCE_EXCP_COMM_DSC LIKE '%DUP%') WITH UR

DECLARE CURSOR1 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_POLICY_NUMBER, CM_CLAIM_NUMBER, CM_USER_LOGON, CM_DATE_CLAIM_PAID FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WS-POLICY-NO AND CM_LOB NOT IN ('LT') ORDER BY CM_POLICY_NUMBER, CM_CLAIM_NUMBER, CM_DATE_CLAIM_PAID .

DECLARE CURSOR1 CURSOR FOR SELECT CW_CLAIM_NUMBER, CW_SHEET_NUMBER, CW_POLICY_NUMBER, CW_USER_LOGON, CW_RCVD_DATE FROM CLAIMS_LIABILITY WHERE CW_CLAIM_STATUS = 'L1' ORDER BY CW_USER_LOGON, CW_CLAIM_NUMBER, CW_POLICY_NUMBER, CW_SHEET_NUMBER, CW_RCVD_DATE .

DECLARE CURSOR2 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_CLAIM_NUMBER, CM_SHEET_NUMBER, CM_POLICY_NUMBER, CM_ACT_PERIOD, CM_CLAIM_STATUS, CM_DENIED_REASON1, CM_DENIED_REASON2, CM_USER_LOGON, CM_PENDING_FLAG1, CM_PENDING_FLAG2, CM_PENDING_FLAG3, CM_PENDING_FLAG4, CM_BDOS, CM_DATE_RECEIVED, CM_TOTAL_PAID, CM_TRANS_CODE FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WS-CW-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WS-CW-POLICY-NUMBER AND (CM_SHEET_NUMBER = :WS-CW-SHEET-NUMBER OR CM_SHEET_NUMBER > :WS-CW-SHEET-NUMBER) ORDER BY CM_CLAIM_NUMBER, CM_POLICY_NUMBER, CM_SHEET_NUMBER, CM_DATE_RECEIVED .

DECLARE CURSOR3 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_CLAIM_NUMBER, CM_SHEET_NUMBER, CM_POLICY_NUMBER, CM_ACT_PERIOD, CM_CLAIM_STATUS, CM_DENIED_REASON1, CM_DENIED_REASON2, CM_USER_LOGON, CM_PENDING_FLAG1, CM_PENDING_FLAG2, CM_PENDING_FLAG3, CM_PENDING_FLAG4, CM_BDOS, CM_DATE_RECEIVED, CM_TOTAL_PAID, CM_TRANS_CODE FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE ((CM_ACT_PERIOD >= :WS-CM-ACT-PERIOD-LOW AND CM_ACT_PERIOD <= :WS-CM-ACT-PERIOD-HIGH) AND (CM_TRANS_CODE = 7 OR CM_TRANS_CODE = 9)) ORDER BY CM_USER_LOGON, CM_CLAIM_NUMBER, CM_POLICY_NUMBER, CM_SHEET_NUMBER, CM_DATE_RECEIVED .

DECLARE CURSOR4 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_CLAIM_NUMBER, CM_SHEET_NUMBER, CM_POLICY_NUMBER FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WS-CM-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WS-CM-POLICY-NUMBER AND CM_SHEET_NUMBER > :WS-CM-SHEET-NUMBER .

DECLARE CURSOR1 CURSOR FOR SELECT CC_PLAN_CODE, CC_PHASE_CODE, CC_PLAN_START_DATE, CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE, CC_STATE_OF_ISSUE, CC_LOB, CC_PLAN_UNITS, CC_COVG_POL_TYPE FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :WS-PVB-DATE-DB2 AND (CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE >= :WS-PVB-DATE-DB2 OR CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01') ORDER BY CC_PHASE_CODE WITH UR

DECLARE CURSOR2 CURSOR FOR SELECT PM_PLAN_CODE, PM_STATE_CODE, PM_AGE_LOW, PM_AGE_HIGH, PM_WAITING_PERIOD, PM_POLICY_FORM, PM_START_DATE, PM_MANUAL_FLAG, PM_DEP_COV FROM PLAN_MASTER WHERE PM_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND PM_STATE_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE WITH UR

DECLARE CURSOR3 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_CLAIM_NUMBER, CM_SHEET_NUMBER, CM_DATE_CLAIM_PAID, CM_TRANS_CODE, CM_BDOS, CM_DIAGNOSIS_CODE, CM_CLAIM_STATUS, CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE, CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME, CM_RELATIONSHIP FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CM_BDOS >= :WM-POLYR-START-DATE AND CM_BDOS <= :WM-POLYR-END-DATE

DECLARE CURSOR4 CURSOR FOR SELECT CD_TREATMENT_DATE, CD_BENEFIT_PAID, CD_BENEFIT_UNITS FROM CLAIMS_DETAIL WHERE CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WM-CLAIM-SHEETN AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-BENEFIT AND CD_BENEFIT_PAID <> 0

DECLARE CURSOR5 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_HANDICAP_IND, CM_BDOS FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WM-SEARCH-FNAME AND CM_CLAIMANT_SEX = :WM-SEARCH-SEX AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WM-SEARCH-BDATE AND CM_HANDICAP_IND <> ' ' AND CM_BDOS <= :WS-PVB-DATE-DB2 ORDER BY CM_BDOS DESC

DECLARE CURSOR6 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_STUDENT_FLAG, CM_BDOS, CM_USER_LOGON FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WM-SEARCH-FNAME AND CM_CLAIMANT_SEX = :WM-SEARCH-SEX AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WM-SEARCH-BDATE AND CM_STUDENT_FLAG <> ' ' AND CM_BDOS <= :WS-PVB-DATE-DB2 ORDER BY CM_BDOS DESC
DECLARE CURSOR8 CURSOR FOR SELECT CF_SEQ_NBR, CF_SHEET_NO FROM CLAIMS_OCR_FORMS WHERE CF_CLAIM_NBR = :WM-SEARCH-CLAIM ORDER BY CF_SEQ_NBR DESC WITH UR

DECLARE COVCELL CURSOR FOR SELECT CC_POLICY_NUMBER, CC_PLAN_CODE, CC_PHASE_CODE, CC_PLAN_START_DATE, CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE, CC_LOB, CC_COVG_POL_TYPE FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PHASE_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PHASE AND ((CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE >= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE) OR (CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01')) WITH UR

SELECT CM_DATE_RECEIVED, CM_DATE_PROCESSED, CM_DATE_PENDED, CM_PENDING_FLAG1, CM_PENDING_FLAG2, CM_PENDING_FLAG3, CM_PENDING_FLAG4, CM_DOC_ORIGIN_DSC, CM_ISF_CLAIMTYPE_ID, CM_ISF_CLAIM_CD, CM_ISF_REPEND_IND, CM_SUBM_AGENT_NO, CM_AGENT_REC_DT, CM_AFLAC_REC_DT, CM_AGENT_COVSHT_IND INTO :CM-DATE-RECEIVED, :CM-DATE-PROCESSED, :CM-DATE-PENDED, :CM-PENDING-FLAG1, :CM-PENDING-FLAG2, :CM-PENDING-FLAG3, :CM-PENDING-FLAG4, :CM-DOC-ORIGIN-DSC, :CM-ISF-CLAIMTYPE-ID :CM-ISF-CLAIMTYPE-ID-IND, :CM-ISF-CLAIM-CD, :CM-ISF-REPEND-IND, :CM-SUBM-AGENT-NO, :CM-AGENT-REC-DT, :CM-AFLAC-REC-DT, :CM-AGENT-COVSHT-IND FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_SHEET_NUMBER = :CM-SHEET-NUMBER AND CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :CM-POLICY-NUMBER AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS = 'L1' WITH UR
SELECT CM_SHEET_NUMBER INTO :CM-SHEET-NUMBER FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :CM-POLICY-NUMBER AND CM_BDOS = :WM-SHEET-BDOS

SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PLAN AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE = :WM-COVERAGE-START WITH UR

SELECT MAX(CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE) INTO :WS-COV-STRT-WK-DATE FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PHASE_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PHASE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE < :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE < :WM-TREATMENT-DATE

SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PLAN AND CC_COVG_POL_TYPE = :CONT-COVRGTYPE-CD WITH UR

SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PLAN AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE = :WM-PREV-COV-START AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01' WITH UR

UPDATE CLAIMS_COVERAGE SET CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = :WM-CALC-STOP-DATE, CC_DATE_CHANGED = :CC-DATE-CHANGED, CC_LOGON_CHANGED = :CC-LOGON-CHANGED WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PLAN AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE = :WM-PREV-COV-START

SELECT MAX(CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE) INTO :WS-COV-STRT-WK-DATE FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PHASE_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PHASE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE < :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE < :WM-TREATMENT-DATE

SELECT MIN(CC_PLAN_START_DATE) INTO :WS-COV-STOP-WK-DATE FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PHASE_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PHASE AND (CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE > :WM-TREATMENT-DATE OR CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01') AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE > :WM-TREATMENT-DATE

DECLARE CURSOR16 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_WITTS_ID, CM_SUBM_AGENT_NO FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WM-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS = 'L1'

DECLARE CURSOR18 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_CLAIM_NUMBER, CM_SHEET_NUMBER, CM_DATE_CLAIM_PAID, CM_TRANS_CODE, CM_BDOS, CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME, CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE, CM_CLAIMANT_AGE, CM_CLAIMANT_SEX, CM_DIAGNOSIS_CODE FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CM_RELATIONSHIP = :WM-SEARCH-RELATIONSHIP AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WM-SEARCH-FNAME AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WM-SEARCH-BIRTHDATE AND CM_BDOS >= :WM-POLYR-START-DATE AND CM_BDOS <= :WM-POLYR-END-DATE ORDER BY CM_DATE_CLAIM_PAID

DECLARE CURSOR19 CURSOR FOR SELECT WB_START_DT, WB_DIAGNOSIS_CODE, WB_TEST_CODE, WB_PAYMENT_NOTE, WB_PLAN_CODE, WB_BENEFIT_AMOUNT, WB_BENEFIT_DATE, WB_BENEFIT_CODE, WB_PER_UNIT_IND, WB_ACTUAL_CHG_IND, WB_CAL_POL_YR_IND, WB_WP_EXCP_IND, WB_MMGRAM_MAX_AMT, WB_2ND_BENEFIT_AMT, WB_ENDORSEMENT_IND FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_POLICY_FORM_TXT = :WM-SEARCH-FORM AND WB_TEST_CODE = :WM-HOLD-TEST-CODE AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE NOT IN (:WK-BEN-PAID-ALREADY) AND WB_START_DT = (SELECT MAX(WB_START_DT) FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_POLICY_FORM_TXT = :WM-SEARCH-FORM AND WB_TEST_CODE = :WM-HOLD-TEST-CODE AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE NOT IN (:WK-BEN-PAID-ALREADY) AND WB_START_DT <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE) WITH UR

DECLARE CRSR_SCOPE CURSOR FOR SELECT WB_START_DT, WB_DIAGNOSIS_CODE, WB_TEST_CODE, WB_PAYMENT_NOTE, WB_PLAN_CODE, WB_BENEFIT_AMOUNT, WB_BENEFIT_DATE, WB_BENEFIT_CODE, WB_PER_UNIT_IND, WB_ACTUAL_CHG_IND, WB_CAL_POL_YR_IND, WB_WP_EXCP_IND, WB_MMGRAM_MAX_AMT, WB_2ND_BENEFIT_AMT, WB_ENDORSEMENT_IND FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_POLICY_FORM_TXT = :WM-SEARCH-FORM AND WB_TEST_CODE IN (:WS-COLON, :WS-SIGMD) AND WB_START_DT = (SELECT MAX(WB_START_DT) FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_POLICY_FORM_TXT = :WM-SEARCH-FORM AND WB_TEST_CODE IN (:WS-COLON, :WS-SIGMD) AND WB_START_DT <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE) ORDER BY WB_TEST_CODE WITH UR

SELECT ST_TABLE_ALIAS2, ST_TABLE_ALIAS4 INTO :WH-TABLE-ALIAS2, :WH-TABLE-ALIAS4 FROM SECURITY_TABLE WHERE ST_SYSTEM_NAME = :WM-SYSTEM-NAME AND ST_TABLE_NAME = :WM-TABLE-NAME AND ST_TABLE_VALUE = :WM-TABLE-VALUE WITH UR

SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PLAN AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE = :WM-PREV-COV-START AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01' AND CC_PHASE_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PHASE WITH UR

SELECT MAX(CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE) INTO :WS-COV-STRT-WK-DATE FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PHASE_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PHASE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE < :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE < :WM-TREATMENT-DATE

SELECT MIN(CC_PLAN_START_DATE) INTO :WS-COV-STOP-WK-DATE FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PHASE_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PHASE AND (CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE > :WM-TREATMENT-DATE OR CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01') AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE > :WM-TREATMENT-DATE

SELECT PM_PLAN_CODE, PM_STATE_CODE, PM_AGE_LOW, PM_AGE_HIGH, PM_WAITING_PERIOD, PM_POLICY_FORM, PM_START_DATE, PM_MANUAL_FLAG, PM_DEP_COV, PM_DEPCOV_STU INTO :PM-PLAN-CODE, :PM-STATE-CODE, :PM-AGE-LOW, :PM-AGE-HIGH, :PM-WAITING-PERIOD, :PM-POLICY-FORM, :PM-START-DATE, :PM-MANUAL-FLAG, :PM-DEP-COV, :PM-DEPCOV-STU FROM PLAN_MASTER WHERE PM_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND PM_STATE_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND PM_START_DATE = (SELECT MAX(PM_START_DATE) FROM PLAN_MASTER WHERE PM_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND PM_STATE_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND PM_START_DATE <= :WM-SEARCH-DATE) FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY WITH UR
SELECT ST_TABLE_ALIAS7 INTO :WH-TABLE-ALIAS7 FROM SECURITY_TABLE WHERE ST_SYSTEM_NAME = 'CLAIMS' AND ST_TABLE_NAME = 'STATE-CODES' AND ST_TABLE_VALUE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE WITH UR

SELECT CM_CLAIM_NUMBER, CM_SHEET_NUMBER, CM_DATE_CLAIM_PAID, CM_TRANS_CODE INTO :WM-CLAIM-NO, :WM-SHEET-NO, :WM-PRIOR-DATE-PD, :WM-TRANS-CODE FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS = 'PC' AND CM_LOB = 'CA' AND CM_DEATH_CODE = ' ' AND CM_DATE_OF_DEATH = '1900-01-01' AND CM_CLAIM_TYPE = 'CT' AND CM_DISABILITY_TYPE IN ('01','03') AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WM-SEARCH-FNAME AND CM_RELATIONSHIP = :WM-SEARCH-RELATIONSHIP AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WM-SEARCH-BIRTHDATE FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
SELECT WELLNESS_PROC_CD INTO :WM-PROC-CD FROM CLAIMS_WELL_PROC WHERE CLAIM_NBR = :WM-CLAIM-NO AND SHEET_NBR = :WM-SHEET-NO AND WELLNESS_PROC_CD = :WM-WELLNESS-PROC-CD FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE = 'WLB' WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE = 'PAP' WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE = 'MMG' WITH UR

SELECT WB_POLICY_FORM_TXT INTO :WM-POLICY-FORM FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE = 'MMG' AND WB_TEST_CODE = 'MAMMO' WITH UR

SELECT CM_CLAIM_NUMBER, CM_SHEET_NUMBER, CM_DATE_CLAIM_PAID, CM_TRANS_CODE, CM_BDOS, CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME, CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE, CM_CLAIMANT_SEX, CM_DIAGNOSIS_CODE INTO :WM-CLAIM-NO, :WM-SHEET-NO, :WM-PRIOR-DATE-PD, :WM-TRANS-CODE, :WM-PRIOR-BDOS, :WM-CLAIMANT-FNAME, :WM-CLAIMANT-BDATE, :WM-CLAIMANT-SEX, :WM-DIAGNOSIS-CODE FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CM_RELATIONSHIP = :WM-SEARCH-RELATIONSHIP AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS IN ('P9','PC') AND CM_BDOS >= :WM-START-DOS AND CM_BDOS <= :WM-END-DOS WITH UR

SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS ^= 'L1'
DELETE FROM CLAIMS_WELL_PROC WHERE CLAIM_NBR = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER
DELETE FROM CLAIMS_DETAIL WHERE CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WM-CLAIM-SHEETN

DELETE FROM CLAIMS_LIABILITY WHERE CW_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER

DECLARE CURSOR10 CURSOR FOR SELECT CF_SEQ_NBR FROM CLAIMS_OCR_FORMS WHERE CF_CLAIM_NBR = :WM-SEARCH-CLAIM WITH UR

DECLARE CURSOR11 CURSOR FOR SELECT CC_PLAN_CODE, CC_PLAN_START_DATE, CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE, CC_STATE_OF_ISSUE, CC_LOB, CC_PLAN_UNITS FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE ORDER BY CC_PLAN_START_DATE WITH UR

DECLARE CURSOR14 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_CLAIM_NUMBER, CM_SHEET_NUMBER, CM_DATE_CLAIM_PAID, CM_TRANS_CODE, CM_BDOS, CM_DIAGNOSIS_CODE FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CM_BDOS >= :WM-POLYR-START-DATE AND CM_BDOS < :WM-POLYR-END-DATE ORDER BY CM_DATE_CLAIM_PAID

DECLARE CURSOR15 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_DATE_RECEIVED, CM_DATE_PROCESSED, CM_DATE_PENDED, CM_PENDING_FLAG1, CM_PENDING_FLAG2, CM_PENDING_FLAG3, CM_PENDING_FLAG4, CM_EMAIL_ADDR_TXT, CM_WEB_SUBMISSION_DT, CM_EXCP_ADDR_IND, CM_ISF_CLAIM_CD, CM_ISF_REPEND_IND, CM_HANDICAP_IND, CM_PROOF_LOSS_DT, CM_DOC_ORIGIN_DSC, CM_ISF_CLAIMTYPE_ID, CM_SUBM_AGENT_NO, CM_AGENT_REC_DT, CM_AFLAC_REC_DT, CM_AGENT_COVSHT_IND FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WM-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS = 'L1'
DECLARE CURSOR16 CURSOR FOR SELECT CM_WITTS_ID, CM_SUBM_AGENT_NO FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WM-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS = 'L1'

DECLARE CURSOR17 CURSOR FOR SELECT WB_START_DT, WB_DIAGNOSIS_CODE, WB_TEST_CODE, WB_PAYMENT_NOTE, WB_PLAN_CODE, WB_BENEFIT_AMOUNT, WB_BENEFIT_DATE, WB_BENEFIT_CODE, WB_PER_UNIT_IND, WB_CAL_POL_YR_IND, WB_WP_EXCP_IND, WB_ENDORSEMENT_IND FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_POLICY_FORM_TXT = :WM-SEARCH-FORM AND WB_TEST_CODE = :WM-HOLD-TEST-CODE AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE NOT IN (:WK-BEN-PAID-ALREADY) AND WB_START_DT = (SELECT MAX(WB_START_DT) FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_POLICY_FORM_TXT = :WM-SEARCH-FORM AND WB_TEST_CODE = :WM-HOLD-TEST-CODE AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE NOT IN (:WK-BEN-PAID-ALREADY) AND WB_START_DT <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE) WITH UR

DECLARE COVCELL CURSOR FOR SELECT CC_POLICY_NUMBER, CC_PLAN_CODE, CC_PHASE_CODE, CC_PLAN_START_DATE, CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE, CC_LOB, CC_COVG_POL_TYPE FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PHASE_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PHASE AND ((CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE >= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE) OR (CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01')) WITH UR
SELECT CC_CURRENT_DATE, CC_RECEIVED_DATE INTO :WH-CURRENT-DATE, :WH-RECEIVED-DATE FROM CLAIMS_CONTROL WHERE CC_CONTROL_KEY = :WM-CONTROL-KEY WITH UR
SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WM-CLAIM-NUMBER

SELECT ST_TABLE_ALIAS2, ST_TABLE_ALIAS4 INTO :WH-TABLE-ALIAS2, :WH-TABLE-ALIAS4 FROM SECURITY_TABLE WHERE ST_SYSTEM_NAME = :WM-SYSTEM-NAME AND ST_TABLE_NAME = :WM-TABLE-NAME AND ST_TABLE_VALUE = :WM-TABLE-VALUE WITH UR
SELECT MAX(CM_SHEET_NUMBER) INTO :CM-SHEET-NUMBER FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER

SELECT CM_PROOF_LOSS_DT, CM_WEB_SUBMISSION_DT, CM_ISF_CLAIM_CD, CM_DOC_ORIGIN_DSC, CM_DATE_PROCESSED, CM_SUBM_AGENT_NO, CM_AGENT_REC_DT, CM_AFLAC_REC_DT, CM_AGENT_COVSHT_IND INTO :WM-HOLD-PROOF-LOSS-DT, :WM-HOLD-WEB-SUBMISSION-DT, :WM-HOLD-ISF-CLAIM-CD, :WS-HOLD-DOC-ORIGIN-DSC, :WM-HOLD-DATE-PROCESSED, :WS-HOLD-SUBM-AGT-NUM, :WS-HOLD-AGENT-REC-DT, :WS-HOLD-AFLAC-REC-DT, :WS-HOLD-COVSHT-IND FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_SHEET_NUMBER = '0101'
SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PLAN AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE = :WM-COVERAGE-START WITH UR
SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PLAN AND CC_COVG_POL_TYPE = :WM-COVG-POL-TYPE WITH UR

SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PLAN AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE = :WM-PREV-COV-START AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01' WITH UR

UPDATE CLAIMS_COVERAGE SET CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = :WM-CALC-STOP-DATE, CC_DATE_CHANGED = :CC-DATE-CHANGED, CC_LOGON_CHANGED = :CC-LOGON-CHANGED WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PLAN AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE = :WM-PREV-COV-START

SELECT MAX(CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE) INTO :WS-COV-STRT-WK-DATE FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PHASE_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PHASE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE < :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE < :WM-TREATMENT-DATE

SELECT MIN(CC_PLAN_START_DATE) INTO :WS-COV-STOP-WK-DATE FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-COVERAGE-POLICY AND CC_PHASE_CODE = :WM-COVERAGE-PHASE AND (CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE > :WM-TREATMENT-DATE OR CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01') AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE > :WM-TREATMENT-DATE

INSERT INTO CLAIMS_COVERAGE (CC_POLICY_NUMBER, CC_PLAN_CODE, CC_PHASE_CODE, CC_PLAN_START_DATE, CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE, CC_STATE_OF_ISSUE, CC_STATE_OF_RES, CC_LOB, CC_PLAN_UNITS, CC_AGENT_NUMBER, CC_DATE_CHANGED, CC_LOGON_CHANGED, CC_COVG_POL_TYPE) VALUES (:CC-POLICY-NUMBER, :CC-PLAN-CODE, :CC-PHASE-CODE, :CC-PLAN-START-DATE, :CC-PLAN-STOP-DATE, :CC-STATE-OF-ISSUE, :CC-STATE-OF-RES, :CC-LOB, :CC-PLAN-UNITS, :CC-AGENT-NUMBER, :CC-DATE-CHANGED, :CC-LOGON-CHANGED, :CC-COVG-POL-TYPE)
SELECT CONT_COVRGTYPE_CD INTO :WM-COVG-POL-TYPE FROM TBL_PM_CONTRACT WHERE CONT_POLICY_NO = :CC-POLICY-NUMBER AND CONT_COMPANY_NO = :WM-COMPANY AND CONT_STATUS_CD <> '51' WITH UR
SELECT CONT_COVRGTYPE_CD INTO :WM-COVG-POL-TYPE FROM PCPTDB01.TBL_PM_CONTRACT WHERE CONT_POLICY_NO = :CC-POLICY-NUMBER AND CONT_COMPANY_NO = :WM-COMPANY WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_OCR_XREF WHERE CX_TEMPLATE_ID = :WM-TEMPLATE-ID AND CX_FORMCALL_ID = :WM-FORMCALL WITH UR

SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-POLICY AND ((CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE >= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE) OR (CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :WM-TREATMENT-DATE AND CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = '1900-01-01')) WITH UR

SELECT PM_PLAN_CODE, PM_STATE_CODE, PM_AGE_LOW, PM_AGE_HIGH, PM_WAITING_PERIOD, PM_POLICY_FORM, PM_START_DATE, PM_MANUAL_FLAG, PM_DEP_COV, PM_DEPCOV_STU INTO :PM-PLAN-CODE, :PM-STATE-CODE, :PM-AGE-LOW, :PM-AGE-HIGH, :PM-WAITING-PERIOD, :PM-POLICY-FORM, :PM-START-DATE, :PM-MANUAL-FLAG, :PM-DEP-COV, :PM-DEPCOV-STU FROM PLAN_MASTER WHERE PM_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND PM_STATE_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND PM_START_DATE = (SELECT MAX(PM_START_DATE) FROM PLAN_MASTER WHERE PM_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND PM_STATE_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND PM_START_DATE <= :WM-SEARCH-DATE) FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY WITH UR
SELECT ST_TABLE_ALIAS7 INTO :WH-TABLE-ALIAS7 FROM SECURITY_TABLE WHERE ST_SYSTEM_NAME = 'CLAIMS' AND ST_TABLE_NAME = 'STATE-CODES' AND ST_TABLE_VALUE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE = 'WLB' WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WS-COUNT-MMG FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_BENEFIT_CODE = :WS-SEARCH-MMG AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WS-COUNT-PAP FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_BENEFIT_CODE = :WS-SEARCH-PAP AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE <> 'WLB' WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :CC-STATE-OF-ISSUE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :CC-PLAN-CODE WITH UR

SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_DETAIL WHERE CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :WP1-POLICY AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE >= :WM-POLYR-START-DATE AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE <= :WM-POLYR-END-DATE AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE = 'WLB' AND CD_BENEFIT_PAID <> +0

SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_DETAIL WHERE CD_BENEFIT_CODE = 'WLB' AND CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :WP1-POLICY AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE >= :WM-POLYR-START-DATE AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE <= :WM-POLYR-END-DATE AND CD_BENEFIT_PAID <> +0 WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE = 'PAP' WITH UR

SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_DETAIL WHERE CD_BENEFIT_CODE = 'PAP' AND CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :WP1-POLICY AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE >= :WM-POLYR-START-DATE AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE <= :WM-POLYR-END-DATE AND CD_BENEFIT_PAID <> +0 WITH UR
SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM WELLNESS_BEN WHERE WB_ISSUE_STATE = :WM-SEARCH-STATE AND WB_PLAN_CODE = :WM-SEARCH-PLAN AND WB_BENEFIT_CODE = 'MMG' WITH UR

SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_DETAIL WHERE CD_BENEFIT_CODE = 'MMG' AND CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :WP1-POLICY AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE >= :WM-POLYR-START-DATE AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE <= :WM-POLYR-END-DATE AND CD_BENEFIT_PAID <> +0 WITH UR
SELECT COUNT (*) INTO :WM-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS ^= 'L1'
DELETE FROM CLAIMS_WELL_PROC WHERE CLAIM_NBR = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER
DELETE FROM CLAIMS_DETAIL WHERE CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WM-CLAIM-SHEETN
DELETE FROM CHECK_HISTORY WHERE CH_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WM-SEARCH-CHECK
DELETE FROM CLAIMS_LIABILITY WHERE CW_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER
DELETE FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :CM-CLAIM-NUMBER

SELECT CC_PHASE_CODE, CC_PLAN_START_DATE, CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE, CC_STATE_OF_ISSUE, CC_COVG_POL_TYPE, CC_PLAN_UNITS INTO :CC-PHASE-CODE, :CC-PLAN-START-DATE, :CC-PLAN-STOP-DATE, :CC-STATE-OF-ISSUE, :CC-COVG-POL-TYPE, :CC-PLAN-UNITS FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :CROSS-PLAN-CD AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT AND (CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE >= :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT OR CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = :WS-DEFAULT-DATE) FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY WITH UR

SELECT BA_BENEFIT_AMT, BA_MAX_UNITS_NBR INTO :WB-BENEFIT-AMOUNT, :WS-MAX-UNITS-NBR FROM BENE_AMT_CALC_DATA WHERE BA_STATE_CD = :CM-STATE-OF-ISSUE AND BA_BENE_CD = :CROSS-BENEFIT-CD AND BA_PLAN_CD = :CROSS-PLAN-CD AND BA_START_DT <= :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT AND (BA_END_DT >= :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT OR BA_END_DT = :WS-DEFAULT-DATE) FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY WITH UR

SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WS-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_MASTER JOIN CLAIMS_DETAIL ON CM_POLICY_NUMBER = CD_POLICY_NUMBER AND CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = DECIMAL(CONCAT (DIGITS(CM_CLAIM_NUMBER), CM_SHEET_NUMBER),13, 0) WHERE CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS IN ('P9','PC') AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE IN ('EMR','ATX') AND CM_ACCSICK_DEL_DTE = :WS-EVENT-DATE AND CM_ACCSICK_DEL_DTE <> :WS-DEFAULT-DATE AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WS-ORIG-FNAME AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WS-ORIG-BIRTHDATE AND CM_DIAGNOSIS_CODE = :WS-ORIG-DIAG-CODE

SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :WS-COUNT FROM CLAIMS_MASTER JOIN CLAIMS_DETAIL ON CM_POLICY_NUMBER = CD_POLICY_NUMBER AND CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = DECIMAL(CONCAT (DIGITS(CM_CLAIM_NUMBER), CM_SHEET_NUMBER),13, 0) WHERE CM_POLICY_NUMBER = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS IN ('P9','PC') AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE IN ('EMR','ATX') AND CM_ACCSICK_DEL_DTE = :WS-EVENT-DATE AND CM_ACCSICK_DEL_DTE <> :WS-DEFAULT-DATE AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WS-ORIG-FNAME AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WS-ORIG-BIRTHDATE AND CM_DIAGNOSIS_CODE = :WS-ORIG-DIAG-CODE

SELECT CD_BENEFIT_UNITS, CD_BENEFIT_PAID INTO :WS-BENEFIT-UNITS, :WS-BENEFIT-PAID FROM CLAIMS_MASTER JOIN CLAIMS_DETAIL ON CM_POLICY_NUMBER = CD_POLICY_NUMBER AND CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = DECIMAL(CONCAT (DIGITS(CM_CLAIM_NUMBER), CM_SHEET_NUMBER),13, 0) WHERE CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS IN ('P9','PC') AND CM_RELATIONSHIP = :WS-ORIG-RELATIONSHIP AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WS-ORIG-FNAME AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WS-ORIG-BIRTHDATE AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE = :WS-START-DT-X AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE = :CROSS-BENEFIT-CD AND CD_BENEFIT_PAID <> +0 WITH UR

SELECT CD_BENEFIT_UNITS, CD_BENEFIT_PAID INTO :WS-BENEFIT-UNITS, :WS-BENEFIT-PAID FROM CLAIMS_MASTER JOIN CLAIMS_DETAIL ON CM_POLICY_NUMBER = CD_POLICY_NUMBER AND CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = DECIMAL(CONCAT (DIGITS(CM_CLAIM_NUMBER), CM_SHEET_NUMBER),13, 0) WHERE CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS IN ('P9','PC') AND CM_RELATIONSHIP = :WS-ORIG-RELATIONSHIP AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WS-ORIG-FNAME AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WS-ORIG-BIRTHDATE AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE = :WS-START-DT-X AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE = :CROSS-BENEFIT-CD AND CD_BENEFIT_PAID <> +0 WITH UR

SELECT CD_BENEFIT_UNITS, CD_BENEFIT_PAID INTO :WS-BENEFIT-UNITS, :WS-BENEFIT-PAID FROM CLAIMS_MASTER JOIN CLAIMS_DETAIL ON CM_POLICY_NUMBER = CD_POLICY_NUMBER AND CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = DECIMAL(CONCAT (DIGITS(CM_CLAIM_NUMBER), CM_SHEET_NUMBER),13, 0) WHERE CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS IN ('P9','PC') AND CM_RELATIONSHIP = :WS-ORIG-RELATIONSHIP AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WS-ORIG-FNAME AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WS-ORIG-BIRTHDATE AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE = :WS-START-DT-X AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE = :WS-PTB AND CD_PROVIDER_NUMBER = :WS-ORIG-PROVIDER AND CD_BENEFIT_PAID <> +0 WITH UR

SELECT CD_BENEFIT_UNITS, CD_BENEFIT_PAID INTO :WS-BENEFIT-UNITS, :WS-BENEFIT-PAID FROM CLAIMS_MASTER JOIN CLAIMS_DETAIL ON CM_POLICY_NUMBER = CD_POLICY_NUMBER AND CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = DECIMAL(CONCAT (DIGITS(CM_CLAIM_NUMBER), CM_SHEET_NUMBER),13, 0) WHERE CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS IN ('P9','PC') AND CM_RELATIONSHIP = :WS-ORIG-RELATIONSHIP AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WS-ORIG-FNAME AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WS-ORIG-BIRTHDATE AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE = :WS-START-DT-X AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE = :WS-PTB AND CD_PROVIDER_NUMBER = :WS-ORIG-PROVIDER AND CD_BENEFIT_PAID <> +0 WITH UR

SELECT CH_CHECK_AMOUNT, CH_SEQUENCE_NUMBER INTO :CH-CHECK-AMOUNT, :CH-SEQUENCE-NUMBER FROM CHECK_HISTORY WHERE CH_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WS-CH-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CH_CHECK_AMOUNT >= :WS-CHECK-ZEROES AND CH_CHECK_DATE = :WS-DEFAULT-DATE AND CH_PAYEE_CODE = :WS-PAYEE-CD WITH UR

UPDATE TBL_CL_CROSS_TRIGGER SET ORIG_CLAIM_STATUS = :CM-CLAIM-STATUS WHERE CURRENT OF TRIGCUR

SELECT CONT_POLICY_NO, CONT_ISSUE_DT, CONT_WAITPRD_IND, CONT_BILLGRP_NO, CONT_CUSTOMER_NBR INTO :CONT-POLICY-NO, :CONT-ISSUE-DT, :CONT-WAITPRD-IND, :CONT-BILLGRP-NO INDICATOR :IND-CONT-BILLGRP-NO, :CONT-CUSTOMER-NBR FROM TBL_PM_CONTRACT WHERE CONT_POLICY_NO = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CONT_COMPANY_NO IN ('01','02') WITH UR

SELECT CONT_POLICY_NO, CONT_ISSUE_DT, CONT_WAITPRD_IND, CONT_BILLGRP_NO, CONT_CUSTOMER_NBR INTO :CONT-POLICY-NO, :CONT-ISSUE-DT, :CONT-WAITPRD-IND, :CONT-BILLGRP-NO INDICATOR :IND-CONT-BILLGRP-NO, :CONT-CUSTOMER-NBR FROM PCPTDB01.TBL_PM_CONTRACT WHERE CONT_POLICY_NO = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CONT_COMPANY_NO IN ('01','02') WITH UR
SELECT ST_TABLE_ALIAS1 INTO :WS-TBL-ALIAS1 FROM SECURITY_TABLE WHERE ST_SYSTEM_NAME = :WS-SYSTEM-NAME AND ST_TABLE_NAME = :WS-TABLE-NAME AND ST_TABLE_VALUE = :WS-TABLE-VALUE WITH UR
SELECT CM_CLAIM_STATUS INTO :WS-CLAIM-STATUS FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :ORIG-CLAIM-NBR AND CM_SHEET_NUMBER = :WS-NEW-SHEET WITH UR

SELECT CD_PAYEE, CD_SEQUENCE_NUMBER, CD_PROVIDER_NUMBER INTO :CD-PAYEE, :CD-SEQUENCE-NUMBER, :CD-PROVIDER-NUMBER FROM CLAIMS_DETAIL WHERE CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WS-CLAIM-SHEET AND CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :ORIG-POLICY-NO AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE = :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE = :ORIG-BENEFIT-CD FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY WITH UR

SELECT CC_PHASE_CODE, CC_PLAN_START_DATE, CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE, CC_STATE_OF_ISSUE, CC_COVG_POL_TYPE, CC_PLAN_UNITS INTO :CC-PHASE-CODE, :CC-PLAN-START-DATE, :CC-PLAN-STOP-DATE, :CC-STATE-OF-ISSUE, :CC-COVG-POL-TYPE, :CC-PLAN-UNITS FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :CROSS-PLAN-CD AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT AND (CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE >= :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT OR CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = :WS-DEFAULT-DATE) FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY WITH UR

SELECT BA_BENEFIT_AMT, BA_MAX_UNITS_NBR INTO :BA-BENEFIT-AMT, :BA-MAX-UNITS-NBR FROM BENE_AMT_CALC_DATA WHERE BA_STATE_CD = :CC-STATE-OF-ISSUE AND BA_BENE_CD = :CROSS-BENEFIT-CD AND BA_PLAN_CD = :CROSS-PLAN-CD AND BA_START_DT <= :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT AND (BA_END_DT >= :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT OR BA_END_DT = :WS-DEFAULT-DATE) FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY WITH UR

SELECT CD_BENEFIT_UNITS, CD_BENEFIT_PAID INTO :WS-BENEFIT-UNITS, :WS-BENEFIT-PAID FROM CLAIMS_MASTER JOIN CLAIMS_DETAIL ON CM_POLICY_NUMBER = CD_POLICY_NUMBER AND CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = DECIMAL(CONCAT (DIGITS(CM_CLAIM_NUMBER), CM_SHEET_NUMBER),13, 0) WHERE CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS IN ('P9','PC') AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE = :CROSS-BENEFIT-CD AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WS-ORIG-FNAME AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WS-ORIG-BIRTHDATE AND YEAR(CD_TREATMENT_DATE) = YEAR(:ORIG-TREATMENT-DT) AND CD_BENEFIT_PAID <> +0 WITH UR

SELECT CD_BENEFIT_UNITS, CD_BENEFIT_PAID INTO :WS-BENEFIT-UNITS, :WS-BENEFIT-PAID FROM CLAIMS_MASTER JOIN CLAIMS_DETAIL ON CM_POLICY_NUMBER = CD_POLICY_NUMBER AND CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = DECIMAL(CONCAT (DIGITS(CM_CLAIM_NUMBER), CM_SHEET_NUMBER),13, 0) WHERE CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS IN ('P9','PC') AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE = :CROSS-BENEFIT-CD AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WS-ORIG-FNAME AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WS-ORIG-BIRTHDATE AND YEAR(CD_TREATMENT_DATE) = YEAR(:ORIG-TREATMENT-DT) AND CD_BENEFIT_PAID <> +0 WITH UR

SELECT CH_CHECK_AMOUNT, CH_SEQUENCE_NUMBER INTO :CH-CHECK-AMOUNT, :CH-SEQUENCE-NUMBER FROM CHECK_HISTORY WHERE CH_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WS-CH-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CH_CHECK_AMOUNT >= :WS-CHECK-ZEROES AND CH_CHECK_DATE = :WS-DEFAULT-DATE AND CH_PAYEE_CODE = :WS-PAYEE-CD WITH UR

SELECT CM_CLAIM_STATUS INTO :WS-CLAIM-STATUS FROM CLAIMS_MASTER WHERE CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = :ORIG-CLAIM-NBR AND CM_SHEET_NUMBER = :WS-NEW-SHEET WITH UR

SELECT CD_PAYEE, CD_SEQUENCE_NUMBER, CD_PROVIDER_NUMBER INTO :CD-PAYEE, :CD-SEQUENCE-NUMBER, :CD-PROVIDER-NUMBER FROM CLAIMS_DETAIL WHERE CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WS-CLAIM-SHEET AND CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :ORIG-POLICY-NO AND CD_TREATMENT_DATE = :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE = :ORIG-BENEFIT-CD FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY WITH UR

SELECT CC_PHASE_CODE, CC_PLAN_START_DATE, CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE, CC_STATE_OF_ISSUE, CC_COVG_POL_TYPE, CC_PLAN_UNITS INTO :CC-PHASE-CODE, :CC-PLAN-START-DATE, :CC-PLAN-STOP-DATE, :CC-STATE-OF-ISSUE, :CC-COVG-POL-TYPE, :CC-PLAN-UNITS FROM CLAIMS_COVERAGE WHERE CC_POLICY_NUMBER = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CC_PLAN_CODE = :CROSS-PLAN-CD AND CC_PLAN_START_DATE <= :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT AND (CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE >= :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT OR CC_PLAN_STOP_DATE = :WS-DEFAULT-DATE) FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY WITH UR

SELECT BA_BENEFIT_AMT, BA_MAX_UNITS_NBR INTO :BA-BENEFIT-AMT, :BA-MAX-UNITS-NBR FROM BENE_AMT_CALC_DATA WHERE BA_STATE_CD = :CC-STATE-OF-ISSUE AND BA_BENE_CD = :CROSS-BENEFIT-CD AND BA_PLAN_CD = :CROSS-PLAN-CD AND BA_START_DT <= :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT AND (BA_DESC_CD = ' ' OR BA_DESC_CD = :WS-HOSP-EMR) AND (BA_END_DT >= :ORIG-TREATMENT-DT OR BA_END_DT = :WS-DEFAULT-DATE) FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY WITH UR

SELECT CD_BENEFIT_UNITS, CD_BENEFIT_PAID INTO :WS-BENEFIT-UNITS, :WS-BENEFIT-PAID FROM CLAIMS_MASTER JOIN CLAIMS_DETAIL ON CM_POLICY_NUMBER = CD_POLICY_NUMBER AND CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = DECIMAL(CONCAT (DIGITS(CM_CLAIM_NUMBER), CM_SHEET_NUMBER),13, 0) WHERE CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS IN ('P9','PC') AND CM_RELATIONSHIP = :WS-ORIG-RELATIONSHIP AND CM_ACCSICK_DEL_DTE = :WS-EVENT-DATE AND CM_ACCSICK_DEL_DTE <> :WS-DEFAULT-DATE AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WS-ORIG-FNAME AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WS-ORIG-BIRTHDATE AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE = :CROSS-BENEFIT-CD AND CD_BENEFIT_PAID <> +0 WITH UR

SELECT CD_BENEFIT_UNITS, CD_BENEFIT_PAID INTO :WS-BENEFIT-UNITS, :WS-BENEFIT-PAID FROM CLAIMS_MASTER JOIN CLAIMS_DETAIL ON CM_POLICY_NUMBER = CD_POLICY_NUMBER AND CD_CLAIM_NUMBER = DECIMAL(CONCAT (DIGITS(CM_CLAIM_NUMBER), CM_SHEET_NUMBER),13, 0) WHERE CD_POLICY_NUMBER = :CROSS-POLICY-NO AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS IN ('P9','PC') AND CM_RELATIONSHIP = :WS-ORIG-RELATIONSHIP AND CM_ACCSICK_DEL_DTE = :WS-EVENT-DATE AND CM_ACCSICK_DEL_DTE <> :WS-DEFAULT-DATE AND CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME = :WS-ORIG-FNAME AND CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE = :WS-ORIG-BIRTHDATE AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE = :CROSS-BENEFIT-CD AND CD_BENEFIT_PAID <> +0 WITH UR

SELECT CW_CLAIM_NUMBER, CW_SHEET_NUMBER, CW_POLICY_NUMBER, CW_NAME_OF_INSURED, CW_CLAIM_STATUS, CW_TRANS_CODE, CW_REV_ENTRY_IND, CW_USER_LOGON, CW_BDOS, CW_RCVD_DATE, CW_ORDER_TYPE, CW_AGENT_FLAG, CW_CLAIM_FLAG, CW_APPR_CODE, CW_BATCH_NUM, CW_PH_NAME, CW_PH_ADDR1, CW_PH_ADDR2, CW_PH_ADDR3, CW_MISC1, CW_MISC2, CW_MISC3, CW_MISC4, CW_LOB, CW_BATCH_TYPE, CW_DATE_PROCESSED, CW_PH_ADDR4, CW_APPROVAL_AUD, CW_APPROVAL_SEQ, CW_BATCH_AGENT INTO :CW-CLAIM-NUMBER, :CW-SHEET-NUMBER, :CW-POLICY-NUMBER, :CW-NAME-OF-INSURED, :CW-CLAIM-STATUS, :CW-TRANS-CODE, :CW-REV-ENTRY-IND, :CW-USER-LOGON, :CW-BDOS, :CW-RCVD-DATE, :CW-ORDER-TYPE, :CW-AGENT-FLAG, :CW-CLAIM-FLAG, :CW-APPR-CODE, :CW-BATCH-NUM, :CW-PH-NAME, :CW-PH-ADDR1, :CW-PH-ADDR2, :CW-PH-ADDR3, :CW-MISC1, :CW-MISC2, :CW-MISC3, :CW-MISC4, :CW-LOB, :CW-BATCH-TYPE, :CW-DATE-PROCESSED, :CW-PH-ADDR4, :CW-APPROVAL-AUD, :CW-APPROVAL-SEQ, :CW-BATCH-AGENT FROM CLAIMS_LIABILITY WHERE CW_CLAIM_NUMBER = :ORIG-CLAIM-NBR AND CW_SHEET_NUMBER = :ORIG-SHEET-NO WITH UR

SELECT CH_CHECK_AMOUNT, CH_SEQUENCE_NUMBER INTO :CH-CHECK-AMOUNT, :CH-SEQUENCE-NUMBER FROM CHECK_HISTORY WHERE CH_CLAIM_NUMBER = :WS-CH-CLAIM-NUMBER AND CH_CHECK_AMOUNT >= :WS-CHECK-ZEROES AND CH_CHECK_DATE = :WS-DEFAULT-DATE AND CH_PAYEE_CODE = :WS-PAYEE-CD WITH UR

SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :W-SNG-POL-CNT FROM NEW_BATCH B ,NEW_APPLIC A WHERE B.PNGID = A.PNGID AND B.PROC_CYCLE_DT = :W-CUR-CYCDT AND B.NB_SRCE = 'SNG' AND SUBSTR(B.BATCHID, 2, 1) ^= 'V' WITH UR

SELECT COUNT(*) INTO :W-SNG-JTI-CNT FROM NEW_BATCH B ,NEW_APPLIC A WHERE B.PNGID = A.PNGID AND B.PROC_CYCLE_DT = :W-CUR-CYCDT AND B.NB_SRCE = 'SNG' AND SUBSTR(B.BATCHID, 2, 1) ^= 'V' AND A.JET_ISSUED_IND = 'Y' WITH UR

DECLARE RESP-ACTION-CURS CURSOR FOR SELECT T3.APPNUM FROM RESPONSE_ACTION AS T4 INNER JOIN (SELECT T1.A AS APPNUM, MAX(T2.RECORD_DATE) AS RECDAT FROM RESPONSE_ACTION AS T2 INNER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT(APPLICATION_NUMBER) AS A FROM RESPONSE_ACTION) AS T1 ON T2.APPLICATION_NUMBER = T1.A GROUP BY T1.A) AS T3 ON T4.APPLICATION_NUMBER = T3.APPNUM AND T4.RECORD_DATE = T3.RECDAT WHERE T4.DESTINATION_CODE = :DEST-CODE AND RESOLVED_DATE = '' AND RESOLVED_DESK_CODE = '' WITH UR .

DECLARE RESP-ACTION-CURS CURSOR FOR SELECT T3.APPNUM FROM RESPONSE_ACTION AS T4 INNER JOIN (SELECT T1.A AS APPNUM, MAX(T2.RECORD_DATE) AS RECDAT FROM RESPONSE_ACTION AS T2 INNER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT(APPLICATION_NUMBER) AS A FROM RESPONSE_ACTION) AS T1 ON T2.APPLICATION_NUMBER = T1.A GROUP BY T1.A) AS T3 ON T4.APPLICATION_NUMBER = T3.APPNUM AND T4.RECORD_DATE = T3.RECDAT WHERE T4.DESTINATION_CODE = :DEST-CODE AND RESOLVED_DATE = '' AND RESOLVED_DESK_CODE = '' WITH UR .

UPDATE RESPONSE_ACTION SET RESOLVED_DATE = :WS-RSLVD-DATE , RESOLVED_DESK_CODE = '999' WHERE DESTINATION_CODE = :IN-DEST-CD AND APPLICATION_NUMBER IN (SELECT APPLICATION_NUMBER FROM RETURNED_APPLICATI WHERE ACCOUNT_NUMBER = :WM-GROUP-NUMBER)

UPDATE RESPONSE_ACTION SET RESOLVED_DATE = :WS-RSLVD-DATE , RESOLVED_DESK_CODE = '999' WHERE DESTINATION_CODE = '63' AND RESOLVED_DATE < :WS-RSLVD-DATE AND APPLICATION_NUMBER IN (SELECT APPLICATION_NUMBER FROM RETURNED_APPLICATI WHERE ACCOUNT_NUMBER = :WM-GROUP-NUMBER)

DECLARE CLAIMS_UPDATE CURSOR WITH HOLD FOR SELECT CM_POLICY_NUMBER , CM_COMPANY_NUMBER , CM_DATE_CLAIM_PAID , CM_CLAIMANT_FNAME , CD_BENEFIT_PAID , CD_PLAN_CODE , CD_PHASE_CODE , CD_INITIAL_DED , CM_CLAIMANT_SEX , CM_RELATIONSHIP , CM_CLAIMANT_BDATE , C3.CONT_SEQ , CD_CLAIM_NUMBER , CD_SEQUENCE_NUMBER FROM CLAIMS_MASTER AS C1 INNER JOIN CLAIMS_DETAIL AS C2 ON C1.CM_CLAIM_NUMBER = C2.CD_CLAIM_NUMBER INNER JOIN TBL_PM_CONTRACT AS C3 ON C1.CM_POLICY_NUMBER = C3.CONT_POLICY_NO WHERE CM_LOB = 'CA' AND CM_ACT_PERIOD >= :WS-ACT-PERIOD AND CM_DATE_CLAIM_PAID > :WS-CLAIM-PAID AND CM_CLAIM_STATUS = 'PC' AND CD_BENEFIT_CODE IN ('FIP','FID','FPP','FPD') ORDER BY C3.CONT_SEQ FOR FETCH ONLY WITH UR .

DECLARE POLICY_INFO CURSOR FOR SELECT CONT_POLICY_NO, CONT_BILLGRP_NO, CONT_FORM_CD, CONT_STATUS_CD, AHBD_PLAN_CD, AHBD_INFORCE_CD, AHBD_ISSUESTAT_CD, AHPM_OCCUPCLS_CD, CONT_OCCUPATN_CD, CONT_ISSUE_DT, AHBD_QUALIFIC_CD FROM TBL_PM_AHBENDTL BENF, TBL_PM_AHPREMIUM PREM INNER JOIN (SELECT CONT.CONT_SEQ, CONT_POLICY_NO, CONT_BILLGRP_NO, CONT_FORM_CD, CONT_STATUS_CD, CONT_OCCUPATN_CD, CONT_ISSUE_DT FROM TBL_PM_CONTRACT CONT WHERE CONT_BILLGRP_NO = :WS-GROUP ) AS BASE ON BASE.CONT_SEQ = BENF.CONT_SEQ WHERE BENF.CONT_SEQ = PREM.CONT_SEQ AND BENF.AHBF_PHASE_NO = PREM.AHBF_PHASE_NO AND PREM.AHBF_PHASE_NO = :WS-PHASE-PERSON AND AHPM_PERSON_NO = :WS-PHASE-PERSON AND AHBD_INFORCE_CD = :WS-INFORCE5 WITH UR .

SELECT (DATE(:WS-WORK-DATE) - :WORK-DAYS DAYS) INTO :WS-TEMP-DATE FROM SYSIBM.SYSDUMMY1 WITH UR .

DECLARE PULL_ZIP_COUNT CURSOR FOR SELECT DISTINCT CIF_ZIP , CONT_FORM_CD , COUNT(*) FROM TBL_PM_CONTRACT INNER JOIN ( SELECT CUST.CIF_CUSTOMER_ID , CIF_ZIP FROM CIF_CUSTOMER CUST , TBL_PF_LOOKUP LOOK WHERE (CUST.CIF_CUSTOMER_ID = LOOK.CIF_CUSTOMER_ID AND (LKUP_ACTIVITY_CD IN (:WS-A,:WS-D,:WS-P,:WS-R))) ) AS CIF ON CONT_CUSTOMER_NBR = CIF.CIF_CUSTOMER_ID WHERE CONT_STATUS_CD = :WS-STATUS-FIVEONE GROUP BY CIF_ZIP, CONT_FORM_CD WITH UR .
